      "widgets_values": [
        "## 04 — Face Detail Lock (Grok identity first)\n**Base path (works with core ComfyUI):** upscale → gentle downscale for sharpness control → save.\n\n**Optional heavy face restore:** after `INSTALL_CUSTOM_NODES=1`, insert Impact Pack / FaceRestore nodes between upscale and save:\n- Detect face → CodeFormer/GFPGAN at **low** fidelity (0.3–0.5) so Grok identity does not drift\n- Avoid high restore weights; they rewrite Grok faces\n\n1. Load Grok still from `input/`\n2. Keep character DNA locked — do not re-prompt a new face\n3. Output → `output/grok_face_lock_####.png` → Identity Lock / I2V"
      ]
